{
  "texts": [
    "Simultaneously, the growing emphasis on sustainability is prompting the food industry to critically evaluate its environmental impact throughout production processes.",
    "As consumers increasingly prioritize eco-friendly practices, companies must adapt to these expectations to maintain competitiveness.",
    "AI can play a crucial role in identifying environmentally friendly ingredients and sustainable methods during product development, enabling businesses to reduce their ecological footprint while maintaining product quality.",
    "For example, AI-optimized sensory evaluation techniques can predict the flavor performance of various sustainable ingredients, guiding the selection of raw materials that not only meet taste standards but also align with environmental goals.",
    "In particular, AI contributes to the improvement of plant-based food products by addressing sensory limitations that often hinder consumer acceptance."
  ]
}